des: Apartments.com can answer your top questions about renting. For example, you can ask us, “What is a loft?” or, “What is MFTE?” We can even suggest locations to hide a key, tell you what kind of bird is best for your apartment, and explore how much it will cost to rent a one-bedroom apartment in San Diego. If you want to know how to apply for affordable housing, we can explain that, too! Get started now by asking a question that will help you in your rental process.
